- content_for :main do
  %h1 Mayoral Round-up
  %p.conversation_description George and Dan meetup with a panel of Cleveland mayors to discuss potential ways of stimulating the economy throughout the city.
  %select(name="comment[type]" id="comment_type")
    %option Official
    %option Other
  %textarea(name="comment[text]" id="comment_text" rows="3")
    Leave a comment...
  %a.button.tertiary(href="#" title="Save to the Stream") Save
  %hr
  %ul.event-details
    %li
      %strong Event:
      %em Roundtable Q&A 
    %li
      %strong When:
      May 24, 2010, 7:00 PM
    %li
      %strong Where:
      %a.text.button(href="#" title="City Club of Cleveland") City Club of Cleveland
  %ul.thread-list
    %li
      .article.comment
        .meta
          .comment-type Official
          %a.rating(href="#" title="Rate this comment") +0
        %img(src="/images/nemeth-avatar-small.png" alt="Official Comment from George Nemeth")
        %p
          %a(href="#" title="George Nemeth's Profile")
            %strong George Nemeth
          %span.action reported:
        %p.content Dan welcomes the audience and introduces the panelists: |
                   Frank Jackson, Jane Campbell and Michael White.         |
        %p
          %a.text.button.conversation-action(href="#" title="Leave a comment") Leave a comment
          %a(href="#" class="privileged" title="Delete this comment") Delete
    %li
      .article.issue.conversation-ticker
        .date
          %p
            May
            %span.day 05
        %p Started discussing a new issue:
        %p
          %a(href="#" title="Starting talking about creating new jobs in Cuyahoga County")
            Creating New Jobs in Cuyahoga County
    %li
      .article.comment
        .meta
          .comment-type.unofficial
          %a.rating(href="#" title="Rate this comment") +0
        %img(src="/images/wilson-avatar-small.png" alt="Unofficial Comment from James Wilson")
        %p
          %a(href="#" title="James Wilson's Profile")
            %strong James Wilson
          %span.action commented:
        %p.content I can't believe Frank Jackson shows up to this event wearing a Yankee's hat. Seriously?
        %p
          %a.text.button.conversation-action(href="#" title="Reply") Reply
          %a(href="#" class="privileged" title="Delete this comment") Delete
      %ul 
        %li
          .article.comment
            .meta
              .comment-type.unofficial
              %a.rating(href="#" title="Rate this comment") +0
            %img(src="/images/wilson-avatar-small.png" alt="Unofficial Comment from James Wilson")
            %p
              %a(href="#" title="James Wilson's Profile")
                %strong James Wilson
              %span.action commented:
            %p.content I can't believe Frank Jackson shows up to this event wearing a Yankee's hat. Seriously?
            %p
              %a.text.button.conversation-action(href="#" title="Reply") Reply
              %a(href="#" class="privileged" title="Delete this comment") Delete
    %li
      .article.comment
        .meta
          .comment-type.question
          %a.rating.positive(href="#" title="Rate this comment") +13
        %img(src="/images/fiorini-avatar-small.png" alt="Question from Joe Fiorini")
        %p
          %a(href="#" title="Joe Fiorini's Profile")
            %strong Joe Fiorini
          %span.action asked a question to:
          %a.question_recipient(href="#" title="Frank Jackson's Profile")
            Frank Jackson   
        %p.content
          Mayor Jackson: 
          %br 
          Why did you put a stop to the proposed Apple Multimedia lab downtown?
        %p
          %a.button.answer(href="#" title="Answer Joe's Question") Answer
          %a(href="#" class="privileged" title="Delete this comment") Delete
